1️⃣ Project Title
Smart Semantic ATS Resume Analyzer
2️⃣ The Problem
Traditional ATS (Applicant Tracking Systems) rely on simple keyword matching to filter resumes. This often causes qualified candidates to be rejected if they use different wording for the same skills. Recruiters also face fatigue when reviewing hundreds of resumes manually, which leads to missed talent and inefficient hiring.
3️⃣ The Solution
Our system uses semantic understanding instead of simple keyword matching to analyze resumes. It converts resumes into structured profiles including skills, experience, certifications, and projects. The system compares candidates with job descriptions, ranks them based on relevance, and explains why a candidate is a good match. This helps recruiters quickly identify the best candidates.
4️⃣ Tech Stack
Python
FastAPI
React (Frontend)
PostgreSQL
NLP / AI Models
Resume Parsing Libraries
